	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64340483"><p>I find the second movie to be even more interesting than the first as it asks an even more important question: Are you truly free?<br>The first one was about the simulation keeping people in a perpetual slumber, with only a rare few trying to wake up. The second one is about those who wake up and try to rebel discovering that rebelling is PART of the simulation. You're there fighting your jailer in this little arena he setup for you to safely blow off steam while you pat yourself on the back for being such a good rebel.<br>The parallels with our world's activist crowd is staggering.</p></div>
